cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent

Class AgentParameters

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.cuni.mff.kocur.agent.AgentParameters

  • public class AgentParameters
extends java.lang.Object
    AgentParameters for entities. They are stored inside map that uses entity's class as a key and EntityParameters as a value. Those can be later retrieved by entitites/agents and can store any type of information. For now the EntityParameter class is empty, but I extend in example agent implementation. There I store propagation functions, that depend on a class name and a team of the entity. The same principle is applied for Interests.
    Author:
    kocur
